    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is literally impossible to reach and i hate being woken up at 3am if my sugar spikes. since i barely ate, my glucose is like 105 right now. if i just skip the basal tonight, isn't it way safer than accidentally bottoming out because i took a full dose when i didn't need it? it feels like common sense to just skip it if there's no food to process.",
